Package: sdtop
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Terminal-based systemd service manager
 sdtop is an interactive terminal application for managing systemd services.
 .
 Features:
  - View all systemd services with color-coded status
  - Real-time log streaming from journald
  - Process tree visualization
  - Start, stop, restart, enable, disable services
  - Filter services by state (running, failed, all)
  - Keyboard-driven interface with vi-style shortcuts
